org.kepler.kar

Class KARCacheManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.kar.KARCacheManager

  • public class KARCacheManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a singleton class to help manage KARs as they are stored in the cache.
    Author:
    Aaron Schultz

        Returns:

      • insertIntoCache

        public boolean insertIntoCache(KARFile karFile)
        Insert a KARFile into the KARS_CACHED table. Called from KARFile class. This method DOES NOT insert any of the entries into the cache. Use insertEntryIntoCache and CacheManager.insertObject
        Parameters:
        karFile -
        Returns:
        true if and only if the kar was inserted false if already exists or error
